Player presses 'g' key or something.
Selected unit enters 'pick_up_mode'.
Player left clicks on tile he wants to pick something up from.
If there is more than one item on it, a menu pops up asking him what he'd like to pick up.
And finally, the unit goes to pick up the...whatever it is the player told it to pick up.

Rubble can be picked up, carried, transported, etc and used in stone constructions.
Like, sealing up leaks, reinforcing a cavern, making bridges, defensive walls, etc.
